profile:
Poseidon Pool Service is the Solar Pool Heating Specialist in Ottawa. We are also your Pool Experts for Service and Repair since 2009. We are fully insured and committed to unparalleled Customer-Focused Service!

If you need your Pool or Solar Pool Heating System serviced this Summer or perhaps you need Advice on your Pool, please Contact us Today!

Our Pool Service is specialized in the Repair, Installation or Replacement of: Pumps, Heaters, Filters, Lighting, Solar Pool Heating Systems, Pipes, Skimmers, Liners and Leak Detection. We are experts at switching your Fresh-Water Pool to Salt Water, and know all about Electronic Chlorine Generators (ECG). Furthermore, we install Pool Automation/Remote Pool Management from your Tablet or Smartphone, perform Pool Inspections and install Mesh or Solid Safety Winter Pool Covers as well as Automatic Covers. We can install Energy saving Solar Pool Heating Collectors, and detect Leaks by using our sophisticated Electronic Leak Detection Equipment.
